\c 10
\s Israeri vachatorerwa maaritari avo namambo wavo
\p
\v 1 VaIsraeri muzambiringa unotanda zvakanaka, unobereka zvibereko zvawo; zvibereko zvavo zvakati zvichiwanda, vakawanzawo maaritari avo; nyika yavo yakati ichifara, ivo vakazviitirawo shongwe dzakanaka.
\v 2 Mwoyo yavo inonyengera, zvino vachapiwa mhaka; acharova maaritari avo, achaparadza shongwe dzavo.
\v 3 Zvirokwazvo, zvino vachati: Hatina mambo, nokuti hatityi Jehovha; kana ari mambo angatiitireiko?
\v 4 Vanotaura mashoko asina maturo, vanopika nhema pakuita kwavo sungano; naizvozvo kutongwa kwavo kunomera somuti unouraya mumihoronga yomunda.
\v 5 Vagere Samaria vachatya mhuru dzeBhetiavheni; nokuti vanhu varo vachaichema, navapristi varo vaiifarira, nokuda kokukudzwa kwayo, nokuti kwabva kwairi.
\v 6 Ichaiswawo Asiriya, chive chipo chamambo Jarebhi; Efuremu vachanyadziswa, Israeri vachanyadziswa namano avo.
\v 7 Kana riri Samaria, mambo waro waparadzwa sechipande pamusoro pemvura.
\v 8 Nzvimbo dzakakwirira dzeAvheniwo, izvo zvivi zVaIsraeri, dzichaparadzwa; munzwa norukato zvichamera pamaaritari avo; zvino vachati kumakomo: Tifukidzei, nokuzvikomo: Wirai pamusoro pedu.
\v 9 Aiwa, Israeri, makatadza kubva pamazuva eGibhiya; ndipo pavakamira; ko vachakundwa nehondo inorwa navana vezvakaipa paGibhiya here?
\p
\v 10 Nguva yandinoda ndichavaranga; marudzi avanhu achavaunganira kana vakasungirwa pazvisakarurama zvavo zviviri.
\v 11 Efuremu itsiru rakapingudzwa, rinofarira kupura zviyo; asi ini ndimene ndasvika pamutsipa waro wakanaka, ndaisa mutasvi pamusoro paEfuremu; Judha vacharima, Jakove achaputsa mavhinga ake.
\v 12 Zvidzvarirei mukururama, mugocheka zvorudo; undai makombo enyu, nokuti inguva yokutsvaka Jehovha, kusvikira achiuya achikunisirai zvakarurama.
\v 13 Makarima zvakashata, makacheka zvakaipa, makadya zvibereko zvenhema, nokuti makange muchivimba nenzira yenyu, uye nokuwanda kwemhare dzenyu.
\v 14 Naizvozvo bope richamuka pakati pavanhu venyu, nhare dzenyu dzese dzichaparadzwa, Sharimani sezvaakaparadza Bhetiaribheri nezuva rokurwa, mai vakaputsanyiwa pamwe chete navana vavo.
\v 15 Ndizvo zvamuchaitirwa neBheteri nemhaka yokushata kwenyu kukuru; mambo waIsraeri achaparadzwa chose mambakwedza.
